{"tid":2322452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"趙斗淳妻請願書曝光：「他是懂禮貌的人」！","createTime":"2020-12-12T10:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T10:43:38.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba92091a58d7edb61a4ce2f1decc40fdc27d59c1","tid":2322452,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:33:46.000Z","msg":"南韓《慶北新聞》、《畿湖日報》報導，有南韓電視台節日前披露趙斗淳2008年首次被移交審判時，他的妻子向法院向提交的請願書內容，提到「老公除了喝酒後會到處遊蕩，在我的內心與家裡人都是非常和平的家庭。」<br />\n<br />\n趙妻稱，有很多人都稱讚趙斗淳是「很懂禮貌」的人，還說他在在家中的行為表現一切良好，結婚20年來，所有家務事都由他一手包辦。<br />\n<br />\n不過根據警方紀錄，趙斗淳一共有17項暴力、竊盜、強姦與殺人等前科，其中就有11起罪行是在結婚後才犯下的。<br />\n<br />\n南韓《JTBC》報導指出，趙斗淳在服刑期間至少寫下100封請願書，但對於當時的犯案過程，趙斗淳一律辯解：「我當時喝醉，不記得了。」每封請願書的最後，都一定會寫上：「請讓我和受害者見面，拜託了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201212/4GEYA5C6BBHH7B3ZDKFCQFJXJU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201212%2F4GEYA5C6BBHH7B3ZDKFCQFJXJU%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jckcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=4299d167\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201212%2F4GEYA5C6BBHH7B3ZDKFCQFJXJU%2F&h=845ead41\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201212/4GEYA5C6BBHH7B3ZDKFCQFJXJU/</a>"},{"pid":"6015285f4637640709f5e783bca3c826ae64ce0d","tid":2322452,"uid":98473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:34:56.000Z","msg":"好有禮貌咁強姦人個女？<br />\n乜野理論"},{"pid":"b25d6a2bb9e777ab5ee1f549d6588141f03ec300","tid":2322452,"uid":37389,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:39:05.000Z","msg":"某程度上佢老婆比佢更恐怖"},{"pid":"6029e80209b1d8b6bde74f75ba5e7b7d83a7202e","tid":2322452,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64bfefce82c0b095efb2eab49860329bd3eb94ac","tid":2322452,"uid":61282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"殺人前科？"}